&lt;a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/447911013?utm_campaign=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_source=rss&amp;utm_content=title" target="_blank"&gt;头部券商营业部后台是不可多得的机会吗?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;
            </description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">cxysdfz</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 15 Feb 2022 12:08:24 +0800</pubDate><guid>http://www.zhihu.com/question/282918151/answer/1465654456</guid></item><item><title>Quant 会有哪些资讯来源？会看哪些博客或者出版物？</title><link>http://www.zhihu.com/question/26108790/answer/2324177300?utm_campaign=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_source=rss&amp;utm_content=title</link><description>&lt;p data-pid="_YeT_D7T"&gt;只写免费的，付费有State Street Associates，Wolfe Research这种，业内人士自然有的看。持续更新。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;社交媒体:&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li data-pid="NSdcKPZx"&gt;Stack Exchange quant版: &lt;a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//quant.stackexchange.com/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;Quantitative Finance Stack Exchange&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-pid="q646VmU_"&gt;Stack Exchange stats版: &lt;a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//stats.stackexchange.com/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;Cross Validated&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-pid="lOpsHWCT"&gt;一些牛人的twitter: 需要自己挖掘&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h2&gt;严肃文学:&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li data-pid="Q1dFvewB"&gt;Arxiv&lt;br&gt;- e.g. JP Morgan已经开始hedge cliquet option的&lt;a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//arxiv.org/abs/1802.03042" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;Deep Hedging&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-pid="J2cyvwyZ"&gt;SSRN&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Blog&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p data-pid="wmh-iSzn"&gt;Rationale: 业界从业者or学界前沿&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li data-pid="lV1xfWXz"&gt;Robert Carver，前Man AHL PM, 现在自己交易: &lt;a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//qoppac.blogspot.com/" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="visible"&gt;qoppac.blogspot.com/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-pid="aLQ7bpjf"&gt;Marcos López de Prado: &lt;a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.quantresearch.org/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;Quantitative Research&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-pid="JPnsXH_J"&gt;Olivier Ledoit: &lt;a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.ledoit.net/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;Olivier Ledoit Homepage&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-pid="HRRrpYef"&gt;Jianqing Fan (No Introduction Necessary): &lt;a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//fan.princeton.edu/research.html" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;Jianqing Fan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Insights from Vendor&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p data-pid="Ef-97YzR"&gt;Rationale: 数据源好，可以做一些fancy的研究&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li data-pid="TB-n5t9u"&gt;Bloomberg: &lt;a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.bloomberg.com/professional/blog/category/quant-research/" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://www.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="visible"&gt;bloomberg.com/professio&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;nal/blog/category/quant-research/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-pid="WJATE7lW"&gt;Refinitiv: &lt;a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.refinitiv.com/en/quant-research%23insights" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;Quant Research&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-pid="ELRje2Qj"&gt;Ravenpack: &lt;a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.ravenpack.com/insights/research/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;Ravenpack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-pid="6pnxMqqq"&gt;Alexandria: &lt;a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.alexandriatechnology.com/insights" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;Insights&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;
